text: Donghaixian railway station (, literally "Donghai County railway station") is a station on Longhai railway in Donghai County, Lianyungang, Jiangsu. ==History== The station was established in 1925 as Niushan railway station (). It was changed to the current name in 1957. ==References== Category:Railway stations in Jiangsu Category:Stations on the Longhai Railway Category:Railway stations in China opened in 1925
